{"tid":1269632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再推烈士post 只會令更多人自殺","createTime":"2019-06-30T15:34:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T17:24:23.000Z","uid":155821,"like":21,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b40100a0458826e7ee25d915cd2e9bc8ea568f59","tid":1269632,"uid":155821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:34:47.000Z","msg":"講明先唔係鬼 只係唔想再有人自殺 一個都嫌多<br />\n<br />\n唔該大家唔好再推啲烈士 post<br />\n講真呢度好多人生經驗尚淺既學生，大部分人對於成個六月既抗爭已經好有無力感<br />\n大家不斷推啲烈士post 尤其是不斷放大啲烈士遺言，只會將絕望同無力既情緒放大 <br />\n講真啲年紀仲細既學生真係未必識處理自己情緒<br />\n而世衛指引一向都叫傳媒報導自殺新聞盡量唔好公開遺書，免得過度渲染想自殺既情緒<br />\n所以大家唔該唔好再推啦<br />\n<br />\n如果大家真係想為烈士做啲嘢既 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">就集中翻聽日七一既行動</span></strong></span><br />\n如果你係有過一走了之既念頭既<br />\n我明白呢場仗係好辛苦 但係二百萬人同你一齊努力緊<br />\n千祈唔好放棄 唔好係呢個政權下低頭<br />\n應承我一齊捱落去好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bbe33e9e6b2b6c4b191a511385a92d453412e0f","tid":1269632,"uid":155821,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:35:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"771801ffc1757c4529c6423b93617168722f7489","tid":1269632,"uid":155821,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:37:09.000Z","msg":"Pushhh"},{"pid":"5bbedf87438cbeb9b88d8fde3bc045c8457aef1b","tid":1269632,"uid":167619,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:37:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JFE35fB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJFE35fB.png&h=759646e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fcf88719c07f6923a8a97959897901f343d52535","tid":1269632,"uid":155821,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:38:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3a2e1b82113aa3690aeb7ea66d1891897446ad5","tid":1269632,"uid":155821,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:39:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e1c8c549f79fce9c3f91e9caac56732703365b2","tid":1269632,"uid":155821,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:40:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6b05db56de80446d859fb3a3b7afe6eb8cf33ec","tid":1269632,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:42:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eGtcYB7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeGtcYB7.jpg&h=492954ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e618dd2a51c1ed7665ad9a79852fa18836a5f239","tid":1269632,"uid":104507,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:43:11.000Z","msg":"阻你少少時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我見到好多post話71 係去示威遊行就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 各位 抗爭左成個月 聽日金紫荊廣場大好機會見到政府高官 點解仲要揀去示威遊行 你地只要行出黎企出黎就幫到啲義士 唔好個個話我唔衝 無人要你衝呀 我地要人數幫啲義士cover呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我求下你地聽日朝早出黎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oa6Vbqx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foa6Vbqx.jpg&h=7af281a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MLcAVSd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMLcAVSd.jpg&h=67b44608&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dyy8wqz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdyy8wqz.jpg&h=18391795&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76756023c6b48dc15ae61ac703718e1f5085e324","tid":1269632,"uid":155821,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T15:44:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea0c